latest_release.name: Version 2.1.0
latest_release.body:
- Regenerate README file [[#244](https://github.com/wp-cli/scaffold-package-command/pull/244)]
- Require framework version 2.11.x [[#243](https://github.com/wp-cli/scaffold-package-command/pull/243)]
- Use a dynamic branch name in the README [[#241](https://github.com/wp-cli/scaffold-package-command/pull/241)]
- Add behat file in the list of files to be copied scaffolding package tests [[#240](https://github.com/wp-cli/scaffold-package-command/pull/240)]
- Add phpcbf composer script in scaffolded composer file [[#238](https://github.com/wp-cli/scaffold-package-command/pull/238)]
- Add `github` option for `--ci` in scaffold package tests [[#237](https://github.com/wp-cli/scaffold-package-command/pull/237)]
- Improve URL validation for scaffold package readme section [[#234](https://github.com/wp-cli/scaffold-package-command/pull/234)]
- Add pre post message example for scaffold readme [[#232](https://github.com/wp-cli/scaffold-package-command/pull/232)]
- Switch up CircleCI dependencies to get tests running again [[#230](https://github.com/wp-cli/scaffold-package-command/pull/230)]
- Fix scaffold package tests command docs [[#229](https://github.com/wp-cli/scaffold-package-command/pull/229)]
- Regenerate README file [[#226](https://github.com/wp-cli/scaffold-package-command/pull/226)]
- Fix typo in package-readme command doc [[#225](https://github.com/wp-cli/scaffold-package-command/pull/225)]
